#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:2
msgid "点击率预测"
msgstr "Click-Through Rate Prediction"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:4
msgid ""
"点击率预测 (CTR Prediction) 模型根据用户和物品的多维特征预测点击概率。 FreeRec 中的 CTR 模型继承自 "
":class:`~freerec.models.base.PredRecArch`。"
msgstr ""
"Click-Through Rate (CTR) Prediction models predict click probability based on multi-dimensional features of users and items. "
"CTR models in FreeRec inherit from :class:`~freerec.models.base.PredRecArch`."

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:8
msgid "DCN"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Deep & Cross Network** — 通过交叉网络 (Cross Network) 显式建模特征间的高阶交互， 结合深度网络 "
"(DNN) 捕捉隐式交互。"
msgstr ""
"**Deep & Cross Network** -- Explicitly models high-order feature interactions through the Cross Network, "
"combined with a Deep Neural Network (DNN) to capture implicit interactions."

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:17
msgid "examples/DCN/main.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:22
msgid "**代码要点：**"
msgstr "**Code Highlights:**"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:24
msgid ""
"**多特征嵌入** ：对离散特征使用 ``nn.Embedding``，对连续特征使用 ``nn.Linear`` + "
"``Unsqueeze``，拼接为统一输入"
msgstr ""
"**Multi-feature Embedding**: Uses ``nn.Embedding`` for categorical features and ``nn.Linear`` + "
"``Unsqueeze`` for continuous features, concatenated into a unified input"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:25
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**交叉网络** ：``CrossInteraction`` 层实现 :math:`x_{i+1} = x_0 \\cdot w^T x_i + "
"b + x_i`，逐层叠加特征交叉"
msgstr ""
"**Cross Network**: The ``CrossInteraction`` layer implements :math:`x_{i+1} = x_0 \\cdot w^T x_i + "
"b + x_i`, stacking feature crosses layer by layer"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:26
msgid "**并行结构** ：Cross Network 和 DNN 并行处理同一输入，最终拼接后通过全连接层输出"
msgstr "**Parallel Structure**: The Cross Network and DNN process the same input in parallel; the outputs are concatenated and passed through a fully connected layer"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:27
msgid "**差异化正则** ：``marked_params`` 对嵌入层和其他参数使用不同的 weight_decay"
msgstr "**Differentiated Regularization**: ``marked_params`` applies different weight_decay values to embedding layers and other parameters"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:28
msgid "**学习率调度** ：使用 ``ReduceLROnPlateau``，根据验证集最佳指标自动降低学习率"
msgstr "**Learning Rate Scheduling**: Uses ``ReduceLROnPlateau`` to automatically reduce the learning rate based on the best validation metric"

#: ../../tutorials/ctr_pred.rst:29
msgid "**训练管道** ：``shuffled_inter_source`` 直接打乱交互记录（非序列），每条记录包含所有特征字段"
msgstr "**Training Pipeline**: ``shuffled_inter_source`` directly shuffles interaction records (non-sequential); each record contains all feature fields"
